			loaded: "‚úì | ƒê√£ load event command \"%1\" th√†nh c√¥ng",
			loadedError: "‚úó | Load event command \"%1\" th·∫•t b·∫°i v·ªõi l·ªói\n%2: %3",
			loadedSuccess: "‚úì | ƒê√£ load th√†nh c√¥ng \"%1\" event command",
