			antiChangeAvatarOff: "ƒê√£ t·∫Øt ch·ª©c nƒÉng ch·ªëng ƒë·ªïi avatar box chat",
			missingAvt: "B·∫°n ch∆∞a ƒë·∫∑t avatar cho box chat",
			antiChangeNameOn: "ƒê√£ b·∫≠t ch·ª©c nƒÉng ch·ªëng ƒë·ªïi t√™n box chat",
			antiChangeNameOff: "ƒê√£ t·∫Øt ch·ª©c nƒÉng ch·ªëng ƒë·ªïi t√™n box chat",
			antiChangeNicknameOn: "ƒê√£ b·∫≠t ch·ª©c nƒÉng ch·ªëng ƒë·ªïi nickname box chat",
